SUMMARY:🍀🎤 St. Patrick’s Karaoke House Party! 🎤🍀
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Movies & Social Group - Celebrating 14 Years!\n🍀
 🎤 **St. Patrick’s Karaoke House Party!** 🎤🍀\n\n**Saturday\\\, M
 arch 14 \\| 8:00 PM – Midnight**\n\nGet ready for a cozy\, high-energy *
 *St. Patrick’s–themed karaoke house party**! Whether you’re a shower
  singer\, a stage star\, or someone who just loves cheering from the couch
 \, this night is all about good vibes\, great music\, and festive fun.\n
 💚 **Dress Code:**\nWearing something **green is highly encouraged** —
  channel your inner Irish spirit! Shamrocks\, hoodies\, hats\, socks… al
 l count.\n🎶 **Karaoke Vibes:**\n\n* Sing your heart out 🎵\n* Or sit 
 back\, relax\, and enjoy the performances\n* All genres welcome — classi
 cs\, pop\, rock\, guilty pleasures\n\n🥨 **Food & Drinks:**\n\n* Some **
 snacks and non-alcoholic refreshments** will be provided\n* **BYOB** if yo
 u’d like alcohol\n* Feel free to bring food or treats to share with the 
 group\n\n📍 **Location:**\nPrivate home **very close to Christie subway 
 station**\n➡️ *Exact address will be shared with all confirmed attende
 es on the day of the party*\n⏰ **Time:**\n**8:00 PM – Midnight**\n⚠
 ️ **Important RSVP Info:**\n\n* **Space is very limited**\n* This is a *
 *private house party**\n* **RSVPs are required and must be respected**\n* 
 Unfortunately\, you **cannot just show up** for this event\n\nIf you’re 
 ready for a fun\, festive\, and friendly night of karaoke\, hit that RSVP 
 and get ready to go green 🍀🎤\n\n***\n\n🎤 **Karaoke Software: Kara
 Fun**\nWe’ll be using **KaraFun** for all karaoke songs — it’s one o
 f the best and most reliable karaoke platforms out there\, with a *huge* l
 ibrary across genres and decades.\n👉 **Check it out here:** [https://ww
 w.karafun.com/](https://www.karafun.com/)\n🎶 **Important — Song Plann
 ing Encouraged!**\nTo keep the night running smoothly and maximize singing
  time:\n\n* Start **thinking about your song choices well in advance**\n* 
 Please **check the KaraFun website** ahead of time to make sure your song 
 is available\n* Feel free to come with **multiple backup songs**\, just in
  case!\n\nYou’re welcome to sing solo\, do duets\, or just enjoy the sho
 w from the audience — no pressure\, just fun vibes 🎉
